OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,FA Belfast barber is feeling lucky to
OL,7,Fbe alive after suffering a brain
OL,8,Finjury and fighting for his life in
OL,9,Fintensive care.
OL,11,FJason 'Jay' Millar went to buy a
OL,12,Fcoffee on Easter Sunday and woke up in
OL,13,Fintensive care three weeks later. He
OL,14,Fhad suffered seizures, fell and
OL,15,Fseriously injured his head, and
OL,16,Frequired life-saving brain surgery.
