OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,FThis is the latest setback for the
OL,7,FJay's Barber Club owner, author and
OL,8,Fvolunteer who has already experienced
OL,9,Funimaginable tragedy in his lifetime.
OL,10,FJason (42) was orphaned and lost his
OL,11,Fbrother Wayne when he was a child, and
OL,12,Fthen found himself in the grip of drug
OL,13,Faddiction.
