OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,FSince then the Belfast man has become
OL,7,Fa prominent social media personality
OL,8,Flocally, making the headlines for
OL,9,Fopening up about his recovery and
OL,10,Ffaith journey. He has also become well
OL,11,Fknown for charitable work including
OL,12,Foffering free haircuts to people
OL,13,Fexperiencing homelessness and
OL,14,Faddiction.
OL,16,FHis recent illness has left him shaken
OL,17,Fbut grateful to be alive and
OL,18,Frecovering.
