OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,FOn April 20th, Jason's wife Orla was
OL,7,Fleft in shock after getting a call to
OL,8,Fsay he had been rushed to hospital
OL,9,Fwhile she was doing an Easter egg hunt
OL,10,Ffor the children.
OL,12,F"It was awful the first few days... It
OL,13,Fwas like hour by hour rather than day
OL,14,Fby day."
OL,16,FUTV asked Orla if she thought Jason
OL,17,Fwould survive.
