OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,F"The first few days I kept asking that
OL,7,Fquestion because I just wanted someone
OL,8,Fto reassure me. But when you can't get
OL,9,Fthat reassurance, it's really hard."
OL,11,FLittle did anyone know that in three
OL,12,Fweeks, Jason would regain
OL,13,Fconsciousness.
OL,15,F"When Orla came up to me, she said,
OL,16,F'do you remember who you are?' I'm
OL,17,Fgoing, 'Why? Why is she talking to me
OL,18,Flike this?' I was just so oblivious to
OL,19,Fwhat happened."
