OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,FAfter several operations, he was
OL,7,Fdischarged and has started a slow
OL,8,Freturn to work, to the delight of
OL,9,Fthose who know him or have been
OL,10,Ffollowing his story on social media.
OL,12,FThere have been thousands of comments
OL,13,Fleft online, while he says well-
OL,14,Fwishers are regularly offering him
OL,15,Fhugs as they are so delighted to see
OL,16,Fhim out and about once more.
OL,18,FHe said: "People are coming up to me
OL,19,Fgoing, 'can I give you a hug? I can't
OL,20,Fbelieve I'm hearing your voice'!"
