OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,FJason said that he has been "near
OL,7,Fdeath's door" many times before, when
OL,8,Fdrinking and taking drugs, and he even
OL,9,Ffell from a three storey building.
OL,11,FHe described this experience as "far
OL,12,Fworse in so many different aspects"
OL,13,Fbut praised the diligent hospital
OL,14,Fstaff for their decision-making, which
OL,15,Fhe says saved him.
OL,17,FJason, who has a strong Christian
OL,18,Ffaith, has managed to find some silver
OL,19,Flinings from this ordeal.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@MO]sD@aOUtD@cO]
