OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,FHe is grateful that he was able to get
OL,7,Fout of his vehicle before the
OL,8,Fseizures, avoiding danger to other
OL,9,Froad users. This is an issue close to
OL,10,Fhis heart as his brother Wayne was
OL,11,Fknocked down and killed as a child.
OL,13,FHe also believes that what happened is
OL,14,Fa sign he needs to slow down,
OL,15,Fsomething that does not come easily
OL,16,Fbecause of his ADHD.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
