OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,F"You work and work and work, but you
OL,7,Fjust work yourself too hard. I'm 42,
OL,8,Fnearly 43. And what I really believe
OL,9,Fnow is that I need to take it slow,
OL,10,Fbecause you can't work like that," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThousands of pounds have been donated
OL,14,Fto a fundraising page since the
OL,15,Fincident, which Jason and Orla have
OL,16,Fdecided to donate to two charities -
OL,17,Fthe NI Children's Hospice and
OL,18,Fhomelessness organisation Teen
OL,19,FChallenge NI.
