OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,FNot everyone has been so kind to
OL,7,FJason. It appears some messages left
OL,8,Fonline have been suggesting he took
OL,9,Fill because of his chaotic past.
OL,11,F"I'm really grateful that they felt
OL,12,Fthe need to leave messages. I know
OL,13,Fwhere they're coming from because of
OL,14,Fthe life I used to have.
OL,16,F"I pray for them and at the end of the
OL,17,Fday, I love them," said Jason.
OL,19,F"If they want to come here, I'll cut
OL,20,Ftheir hair for free, because they know
OL,21,Fthat I am a nice person.
