OL,3,C'Everyone's amazed I'm alive': Barber
OL,4,CJay's close shave with death
OL,6,F"Everybody's got a past, but at the
OL,7,Fend of the day, I'm trying to make a
OL,8,Fdifference in so many different ways.
OL,9,FAnd the reason I've fallen and hurt
OL,10,Fmyself is because I've just worked
OL,11,Fmyself too hard.
OL,13,F"No matter what people say about me, I
OL,14,Fwill still love them and help them."
